data.description: Nicely updated home in the quietest street in Elsa. Nestled just North of 107 this property boasts about 2000 sqft. living, on a 8000+ sqft. lot.  Property has mature trees and storage shed conveys.  There is a bonus room or 4th bedroom with a bathroom en suite.  All bedrooms have ample size perfect for the growing family.  Come see this updated 4 bdrm/3 bath gem.  Well below comps, lets make a deal.
